<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好啊——！<delay frames="30" />
把煙火不斷地發射出去吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也要盡全力享受喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />快看啊！<delay8 />是煙火喔！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然這規模不得了啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay8 />我興奮起來啦——！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來啦來啦——！！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會終於要開始啦！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來盡全力享受吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當煙火射向高空時，<delay20 />
那情景很令人興奮對吧——！？<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好！<delay8 />我的情緒越來越高漲啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要聞到煙火的氣味，<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能切實地感受到<delay8 />
今年也到了<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個季節啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說那些高空煙火<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從側面看會是什麼樣子啊？<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我問你，<delay8 />你知道是什麼樣子嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛剛的煙火好大啊！？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />又大又亮的，<delay20 />一瞬間
我還以為是太陽出來了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">當煙火射向空中時，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我總是會回憶起在起跑線<delay20 />
鳴槍時的聲音啊。<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要想到<delay8 />不知道下一秒會不會發出爆炸聲響，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就不禁心跳加速喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有拿出幹勁來享受煙火嗎！？<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要保持這高漲的情緒<delay20 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直到活動最後一刻喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可別因為<delay8 />煙火差不多要結束了，<delay20 />
就在最後鬆懈囉！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為活動的最高潮，<delay20 />總是在活動<delay8 />
快結束前才開始啊——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 06 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><10_14 arg="0" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="150" />是煙火啊——！！<size value="100" /><delay40 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="150" />好漂亮啊————！！！<size value="100" /><size value="100" /><delay40 /><size value="100" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><10_9 /><pageBreak /><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，你還在等什麼！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能夠靠大吼來鍛鍊腹肌的時機，<delay20 />
就只有現在囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>